      "date": "2013-11-25 01:13:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/b1ab4e7c-556b-11e3-bcc1-52540035b04c).  Ran 19 tests.  No failures.",
